name: Parallel Universe Planet Project #1
description:
Parallel Universe Planet Project is a series of interactive artwork projects for P5JS. Each planet has its own unique physical rules.

Planet #1 is a planet made of flaming iron fragments. Its temperature is very high and there is a strong magnetic field at the top and bottom, causing some of the debris to erupt vertically.

The viewer can click the mouse to create a burning gravity field that increases the temperature of the red planet.
